text:
Metropolitan Avenue, (tracks thereon) at the N.E. corner of Union Turnpike, showing in two views the Autenrieth's Hotel, also known as Alberts Inn in 1923, and Utopian Inn in 1929. A section of this hotel is in the new proposed line of the Turnpike.

October 1923
Views 1 and 2

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection
